const en_translation = {
    general: {
        company_name: "2toring",
        company_name_caps: "2TORing",
        form: {
            first_name: "First Name",
            first_name_placeholder: "Your Name",
            email: "Email",
            email_placeholder: "your@email.com",
        },
        buttons: {
            become_a_tutor: "Become a Tutor",
            login: "Login",
            send: "Send",
        }
    },
    first_fold: {
        the_online_tutoring: "The online tutoring platform for teachers and schools.",
        the_online_tutoring_text: "Provide a face-to-face tutoring experience with video conferencing, screen sharing, interactive whiteboard tools, and much more. Give private lessons or teach groups, with a personalizaed platform for you.",

        the_dynamics: "The dynamics of learning are advancing quickly",
        the_dynamics_highlight: "and so can you.",

        set_your_own: "Set your own schedule",
        set_your_own_text: "Accept sessions when they work for you. Login and be online when you’re free to help students in need of assistance and schedule time slots dedicated for your lessons. As a school you can also create courses and set preferred times to fit your curriculum.",

        be_your_own_text: "2TORing is a platform that connects you with students. You decide which students you work with, when you want to work, and how much you wish to charge.",

        get_paid_weekly_text: "Tutors get paid for lessons each week. Money is deposited directly into your bank account or debit card automatically. We handle all billing issues, making sure you receive payments on time and in full.",

        customize_your_own_text: "Add your branding to keep the platform inline with yours or even get deeper customization if needed. Select different types of themes to suit your needs. ",

        menage_and_monitor_text: "Using a real-time analytics dashboard that provides you with the data you need to understand when your tutoring services are most in demand.",
    },

        register_as_a_tutor_text: "Let us know you’d like to tutor using the platform. Have your teaching credentials, proof of education, and ID ready.",
        add_your_school: "Add your school",
        add_your_school_text: "Make the platform your own with branding and custom modules for billing, catalogs, content and more.",
        set_your_schedule: "Set your schedule",
        set_your_schedule_text: "Set your schedule, sharpen your profile. Make sure you receive the right session requests for you. Set your availability.",

        start_tutoring_text: "Get notified before your sessions start and host your classroom with ease using any webcam or mobile video device.",

        get_schedule_payments_text: "Start earning money tutoring your students online and get paid at the end of each week through our customizable billing system.",

        the_2tor_classroom: "The 2TORing Classroom",

        catalog: "Catalog",
        events: "Events",
